bibtex-tidy-rs

This crate ports non-CLI formatting behavior from bibtex-tidy.

- bibtex-tidy: BibTeX formatting, transform, duplicate, and key-generation behavior. License: MIT. Source: https://github.com/FlamingTempura/bibtex-tidy

The upstream test specifications and corpus are vendored under `testdata/tidy`
for compatibility testing and future benchmark reuse.
